<h4 class="center-align">
  Chicago’s ﬁrst zero-emissions compost collection service for home & business.
</h4>

<table>
    <tr>
      <th>Step 1:</th>
      <th>Step 2:</th>
      <th>Step 3:</th>
      <th>Step 4:</th>
      <th>Step 5:</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>You sign up and we drop off a clean bucket with a fresh compostable liner and lid. </td>
      <td>You fill that bucket with compostable waste such as your food scraps, certified compostable serviceware, and other organic materials.</td>
      <td>You leave the bucket out on pickup-day and we replace it with a cleaned bucket, fresh liner, and lid.</td>
      <td>Your waste is transformed into premium, locally-sourced, black gold, otherwise known as compost.</td>
      <td>The compost gets distributed to community gardens, urban agriculture, or back to you.</td>
    </tr>
